Odaily Planet Daily News: Trader Eugene Ng Ah Sio posted on his personal channel that James Wynn may be a positive figure in this circle: 
1. Let you see the consequences of messing around with leverage; 
2. Help HYPE advertise for free; 
3. Tell you that as long as you are "autistic" and "stupid" enough, making $100 million is not a dream (of course, don't learn from him to lose all the money he made).
